{"tid":1018430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BIGBANG勝利 夜店的工作人員給VIP客戶提供毒品，勝利不再接管拉麵店","createTime":"2019-02-12T08:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T09:34:17.000Z","uid":74065,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"825e5d002720b2508752b95d7072f9004576047d","tid":1018430,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007h1wb4ly1g03ju8h5aej31051hc1kx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F007h1wb4ly1g03ju8h5aej31051hc1kx.jpg&h=00af6c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11日MBC報導了勝利掌管的夜店VIP顧客的證言,說他們被夜店職員勸服吸毒。<br />\n據VIP顧客爆料說:&quot;(俱樂部職員)給了我們藥片之類的東西,並攛掇我說'要不要試一試'。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n此外,去年7月7日,該夜店一名男子喝完某人給的香檳酒後,出現藥物中毒症狀,急救人員立即出動,夜店員工聊天室裡&quot;有人給我下藥&quot;的消息不斷。因該夜店員工出現藥物中毒症狀,警方出動，但已作內查終結處理，對此,警方表示:&quot;雖然簡易檢查結果是冰毒陽性,但國立科學調查研究院精密檢查結果為陰性,所以沒有進行深度調查。<span style=\"color: red;\">最初因暴力爭議而引發的夜店爭議,逐漸擴展為與警方的勾結關係,毒品流通,性交易爭議,而勝利被迫辭去董事職務。</span><br />\n<br />\n當時YG娛樂公司代表楊賢碩表示說:&quot;勝利面臨入伍,為了遵守相關法令辭去了理事一職。<br />\n&quot;據悉,勝利還辭去了該夜店公司內部董事一職。<br />\n<br />\n據公司法人登記簿副本顯示,勝利於今年1月21日辭去公司董事職務。<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/007h1wb4ly1g03jqhffemj30xg1hc141.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F007h1wb4ly1g03jqhffemj30xg1hc141.jpg&h=463c5b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/007h1wb4ly1g03k2a6609j30zu1hctjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F007h1wb4ly1g03k2a6609j30zu1hctjx.jpg&h=dd90dfa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYG大藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有排玩了單野"},{"pid":"8cc93070a01d9487403137a6e771921b358de1af","tid":1018430,"uid":177639,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:51:39.000Z","msg":"唱歌為名 販毒為實"},{"pid":"f6eb2d0b600780142f8b56c4296b2381162403e9","tid":1018430,"uid":81725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"犯罪天團之名當之無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edbae861eac834f211f9a47ffb428863d7a40d0","tid":1018430,"uid":223790,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53271afd97ae6ed9f4ad0f3a218638986a01c386","tid":1018430,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"單野唔係推到上青瓦台了?之後點"},{"pid":"d31e40560a9bd6469be7de1ac8d2406e2927a479","tid":1018430,"uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53271afd97ae6ed9f4ad0f3a218638986a01c386","tid":1018430,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"單野唔係推到上青瓦台了?之後點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"青瓦台個個冇閪死<br />\n李光朱都重未比人處死"},{"pid":"4fbad01b60bf69357f33f2fab2986fe2d0b22ed8","tid":1018430,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"想同勝利做愛 人夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}